This is Lunar 12 to Letheia HQ. Come in. Over. ... We have an emergency HQ - some kind of monster! Come in HQ! ... What's going on!? HQ, can you hea-

^yellow;[INTERRUPTED] This is the Letheia automatic call response. The Letheia Corporation is aware of your situation. Outgoing communications from "Lunar Base 12" have now been shut down. We hope you have a nice day.
The transcript of a failed outgoing radio message with automated lock out response.
